gt; (-a)b 係 (-a)(-b) 嘅相反數<br />\n<br />\nA&amp;B:<br />\n(-a)b+ab = (-a)b+(-a)(-b)<br />\n兩邊Cancel (-a)b<br />\n<br />\nab=(-a)(-b)"},{"pid":"f918931b425975100d766eb9bb050b35075b9ea9","tid":1803293,"uid":33952,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T09:20:51.000Z","msg":"負負得正=反彈你個反彈<br />\n其餘應該唔難諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ae6e2c9fc4a15239f774272a1e768e7a4632cf","tid":1803293,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T07:32:13.000Z","msg":"用field axioms 推出嚟"},{"pid":"2fff1eb447b6c8a3a608728432eaf63968e018e3","tid":1803293,"uid":100412,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T07:43:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mvmuCPvRoWQ?t=610\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmvmuCPvRoWQ%3Ft%3D610&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=ca50f028\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mvmuCPvRoWQ?t=610</a><br />\n唔知幫唔幫到你"},{"pid":"4447321735980600af00bf672684918ccb510f2e","tid":1803293,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T07:54:28.000Z","msg":"唔識  好似話加減 已經解釋到乘除<br />\n<br />\n數學物理d原理全部有得解釋<br />\n<br />\n不過對考試冇用  冇人會理  記住公式先最有用"},{"pid":"26436adc83064d619bf7ef1545f999f0a423d180","tid":1803293,"uid":59623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T08:26:11.000Z","msg":"我用圖片答你<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/trbDW4V.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtrbDW4V.gif&h=0ca3ae55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6769853a181aa46e7e5805f696db7467e6801c64","tid":1803293,"uid":129218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T21:27:03.000Z","msg":"你要知道加法同乘法既公理先（axioms)<br />\n<a href=\"http://mathonline.wikidot.com/the-axioms-of-the-field-of-real-numbers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmathonline.wikidot.com%2Fthe-axioms-of-the-field-of-real-numbe